channel.title: Shpovill!
channel.description:
I have made my own server called shpovill, shpovill2 etc. ends with shpovill5
pass is shpo
It's not the best right now but I'm constantly working and learning so get a spot while you can!
I know this doesn't belong here but i made a tutorial on how to make and join servers at www.freewebs.com/shpovill[br][size=1]Posted at: September 25, 2006, 04:41:39 PM[/size][hr]Info:
My server is on around 3pm-9pm on weekdays. Varies on weekends. I live in Nebraska so the time might be different where you live.
Commands:
::kalph tellies you to kalphite zone ::noclip (you can walk through walls) ::tar ::gotobarrows tar and barrows are mixed up ::barrows all barrows ::range range armor ::melee dragon armor ::mage magic armor ::empty empties your inventory ::gopk tellies you to wilderness ::cw tellies you to cw (you can play it to, if you score u get a christmas cracker) ::mypos shows your position ::players how many players are online ::bank opens your bank ::yell ...... after yell put what you want to say ::fly lets you hover ::tele ####,#### in the #### put a cordinate to tele there ::cannon gives you a cannon as a weapon
you can do ice barrage by clicking on the empty slot next to friends list you can do most normal magic spell without runes to get ure mage up
so far i got monsters in varrock center, real barrows area, tzhaar, near the 3 cages in varrock (with a Tztok Jad), skeletons and guards in varrock castle, mage arena (do the last ancient mage tele and then noclip to get there), and 2 men in the varrock punching bag place that'll kill you in 1 hit.
hope you like my server
